| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3679 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 660b6542-9102-56ad-a1c3-fbf52c49aec7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
